title: Joe Biggs
added: On January 6, Biggs and Proud Boys leader [[Ethan Nordean]] led a mob of Proud Boys members and supporters, as they marched near the Capitol. Biggs used a walkie-talkie to issue instructions, while Nordean used a [[bullhorn]] to communicate with the crowd.
